# Strands Agent Framework

## Rules
- Agent tools (`app/agents/tools.py`) must return Pydantic models (structured outputs)
- Tools should be deterministic where possible
- Agent orchestrates tool calls; tools call domain/data layers
- No business logic in agent layer; delegate to domain

## Enforcement
- All tool return types must be Pydantic models from `app/domain/models.py`
- Agent entrypoint in `app/agents/strands_agent.py` (build_agent function)
